<Content>Truly Awful If you are tempted to stay here based on the price and the location stop right now and find somewhere else.We had booked for three nights but checked out after one when even the guy at reception admitted is was old and dirty. We probably wouldn't have lasted that long if we hadn't arrived at midnight and had nowhere else to go. The walls desperately needed painting what little furniture there was was old and very run down and the noise from La Ramblas rattles against the inadequate single glazed windows. I didn't dare cook anything in the kitchen.I'm no hotel snob but this place is disgusting. 
